             <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f6d8fca7-4fa1-474f-b5ed-ee1716f3bfd0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6090fcd0-d4a1-4fdb-8152-892b137cbf71\">첩약(한약)을 건강보험 적용하기 위한 시범사업이 곧 시작됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-58c7d446-fcca-433f-8d5d-0d8dc588e335\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4c2e1a50-d6a1-439a-995a-b621c0e87d52\">시범사업이 잘 진행되면 첩약(한약) 건강보험 완전시행도 이어서 진행되리라 기대해 봅니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-843b00c9-55d6-4e8a-aa0a-5748a2411cec\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-01a98142-e701-41c6-a00c-0c667c4896eb\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8a36c04c-8b69-4f42-9fe7-f3ae61942706\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bb6640fb-95fc-4366-b09c-9ced5f4ab6e6\">첩약(한약) 건강보험 적용 시범사업에서는 3가지 질환</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-de64b151-9aeb-4c6f-b7b6-f1711dab7d38\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f42bb81c-4f58-452f-b777-21777e8c4f69\">월경통(생리통)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4197112a-3d49-4e82-990d-5d6483d5ccd6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cdf7863d-f29f-4182-bd6f-3faf1e9c1fb4\">중풍후유증</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a918c0a1-92e0-4855-ab8c-45fe8611caee\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e601c06f-51e7-478a-a81b-accd59baaaae\">안면신경마비(구안와사)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a5a80e72-74f4-493d-bab5-59fe2697e719\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6eaf0431-eef8-4fe5-b993-6ea959d68987\">에 대해</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-12bc3259-190e-4b76-9a9a-d28652ee1d80\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e69d7461-97d6-4e78-8ac6-cc82849d84ea\">1인당 1년에 1회에 한해서 건강보험 적용되는 한약을 처방받을 수 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-dfb6233c-6484-43ef-b738-542635f41079\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3337aea1-6b8b-404e-8f7d-3a0929656b05\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b5394887-39ac-4303-b4b8-28f7e0d073bb\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-b5394887-39ac-4303-b4b8-28f7e0d073bb\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMDA5MDFfMjk2/MDAxNTk4OTI5MzY4MzQ1.hYrTGDhyFzIq0EeYiJkB7vGaprjPTryueppKloeAnaMg.JBT2ooXXp2FwzmSYYWWNlrSLxpNSYbkgC-C64y0TEKsg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20200901_115417617.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1125\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1133\", \"linkUse\" : \"fa